rst Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["From Latin <i>Pontius</i>, originally a family name of uncertain origin."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Poncie de Mison, dame de Gordes was born in 1105, in Mison, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France, her father, Bertrand de Mison, was 31 and her mother, Béatrix DE MEVOUILLON, was 31. She married Bertrand I Raimbaud d'Agoult in 1125, in Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died in April 1157, in Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France, at the age of 52."},"et":{"1105–April 1157":"1105–aprill 1157","1105–1157":"1105–1157","1110–1172":"1110–1172","1095–1150":"1095–1150","1130–1203":"1130–1203","–Male":"Surnud","1075–Male":"1075–Surnud","1075–Female":"1075–Surnud","1105":"1105","April 1157":"aprill 1157","1203":"1203","1125":"1125","1157":"1157","1110":"1110","1130":"1130","après 1150":"pärast 1150","1075":"1075","1150":"1150","1095":"1095","1172":"1172","Mison, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Française":"Mison, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Prantsusmaa","Castell d'Agoult, Luberon, Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Française":"Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Prantsusmaa","Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France":"Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Prantsusmaa","Sault, Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France":"Sault, Vaucluse, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1105–April 1157":"1105–huhtikuu 1157","1105–1157":"1105–1157","1110–1172":"1110–1172","1095–1150":"1095–1150","1130–1203":"1130–1203","–Male":"Kuollut","1075–Male":"1075–Kuollut","1075–Female":"1075–Kuollut","1105":"1105","April 1157":"huhtikuu 1157","1203":"1203","1125":"1125","1157":"1157","1110":"1110","1130":"1130","après 1150":"1150 jälkeen","1075":"1075","1150":"1150","1095":"1095","1172":"1172","Mison, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Français